{"type": "article", "id": 20753, "title": "地灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-15T07:17:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606134012LO9ogCRrZGH7JyUY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个小的地面灯，只用了两种材料。圆筒形的灯罩微微朝上，贴着灯罩外有一根弯曲的木结构，与灯罩构成三角的支撑。弧形部分是一个手提杆，方便提着它直接移动，小巧可爱。这盏灯由意大利设计师 Tommaso Caldera 设计，有黑、白、蓝和枣红色四种颜色，售价 340 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.incipitlab.com/products/elma\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134010TVh1mkAYIfRytUFd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134010sJHOxao90TDj7eNB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134011D6YSv8fFnKH0j1eG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134011QcUjG5y0m6NnWIDe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}